channel.title: Long time no talk
channel.description:
Hello Moparscape.
I've been AFK for a while now and thought I'd give an update of what I've been doing to the people who give a fuck!
July 27th 2015 I went to the Navy bootcamp, the Dr there said I broke my leg( he finally looked at the X-Ray and realized he was an idiot) so instead of being at BC for 8 weeks I was there 14. I am currently stationed in the US as a logistics specialist and doing IT work as a collateral duty.
For those who knew, I am still married but probably getting a divorce soon, i'm not fretting over that shit though.
I've been trying to pick the guitar up again lately and below this you can find a video of myself and a friend singing/jamming out.
If you knew me drop a comment and say hello, or if you didn't know me say hello anyways asshole! It's nice to see the community still going!
[youtube]https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ub-rejgklXY&feature=youtu.be[/youtube]

item.description:

WarTusk-RSPS:

Hey Jal I think we met once. Did you work for the Divination of the gods server a year ago? You do web developing I think if I remember correctly. If not Hi anyways lol. Sorry about the Broken leg mate that sucks. Are you going back into the RSPS scene at all?

Hey! Yeah I did some work for them a while back.

I’m not sure If I will be or not. I’ve kind of been stalking the site for the past week now tbh so I may jump back in. My web devo skills have advanced a lot due to school so I may try to help some people out with it.
